body:
I’m Torn

I’m at a weird point with this whole Pretty Rage/Kamen Haida thing. On one hand, I want to get the whole thing done, and release it as one big post. However, on the other, I have set, admittedly, a pretty big structure to how I want it to be set up, and with how I have it set up…..well…

I’m just about halfway done. 😅

So, as a result, I kinda wanna get some feedback. So, guys, lemme ask you, do you think I should hold off starting to post it soon, and later post the whole thing, when it’s done? Or should I release it in 2 parts, so you guys have some stuff to hold you over? Because as it stands, the first half is just about done. I need to write, I think, one or two more sentences, and that will be it.
